y warranty.","Most jewelers will only repair items purchased in that particular store. The ability to make small watch repairs on your watches and bracelets has the advantage of making them usable again without having to find a jewelry repair shop. In addition to making small watch repairs, this kit would also be useful to change batteries in small electronics and tighten or change screws on eyeglasses or sunglasses.","The Jomashop Deluxe Watch Repair Tool Kit includes what you need to make small watch repairs, such as changing or repairing a watchband or changing a battery, at a reasonable price and is versatile enough that you can use the tools for other uses. If you are looking for a versatile watch tool kit, you may wish to check this one out to see if it meets your needs."]},"id":"8cc2efae-4729-49b0-8ba7-77e09ad094b7","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_64062","url":"/jomashop-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"grant-morgan","url":"/author/grant-morgan","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","name":"Grant Morgan","dateModified":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","id":"5h9THR5HH34dskUikqZYj8","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2015-04-09T15:16:42Z","datePublished":"2015-04-09T15:16:42Z","name":"Jomashop 16-Piece Deluxe Watch Repair","synopsis":"The Jomashop 16-Piece Deluxe Watch Repair Tool Kit makes it simple to attach a new watchband, remove links from a metal watchband or bracelet, replace a missing pin or change a battery.","review":{"pros":[""],"cons":[""]},"strapline":"The Jomashop 16-Piece Deluxe Watch Repair Tool Kit makes it simple to attach a new watchband, remove links from a metal watchband or bracelet, replace a missing pin or change a battery.","language":"en","dateModified":"2015-04-09T15:16:42Z","id":"dFF2vgqi55p2cpBFr9jaDo","meta":{"title":"Jomashop 16-Piece Deluxe Watch Repair Review - Pros, Cons and Verdict","description":"Read our unbiased review of Jomashop. See